{"tid":2262331,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"廚師涉5月24日凌晨刑毀大水坑站閉路電視鏡頭 判監三星期 其中一星期與早前另案同期執行","createTime":"2020-10-29T04:53:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-29T08:30:39.000Z","uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"7b476545e966ea894b92891fffbeb079d70810c2","tid":2262331,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T04:53:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/10754\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F10754&d=2u41qa%2Bce9Gslgrzp%2F5KimsgcJLaMXzh2FZp7TjlN88%3D&h=e33058fc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/10754</a><br />\n<br />\n#沙田裁判法院第七庭<br />\n#香淑嫻裁判官<br />\n#審訊 [1/1]<br />\n#20200524馬鞍山<br />\n<br />\n劉 (25)🛑涉另一單案件服刑中<br />\n<br />\n控罪：刑事損壞<br />\n被控於2020年5月24日在馬鞍山大水坑港鐵站A出口行人隧道內，無合法辯解而損壞一個屬於香港鐵路有限公司的閉路電視鏡頭，意圖損壞該財產或罔顧該財產是否會被損壞。<br />\n<br />\n案情：<br />\n2020年5月24日凌晨約1時，警方港鐡大水坑站內控制室，發覺站外一條行人隧道內的一部閉路電視遭到破壞，經無線電通知附近警員，有警員發現被告並跟縱回家，在屋苑樓下拘捕被告。<br />\n<br />\n提堂<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/7906\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F7906&d=2u41qa%2Bce9Gslgrzp%2F5KimsgcJLaMXzh2FZp7TjlN88%3D&h=00fbe32d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/7906</a><br />\n<br />\n❗️被告認罪❗️<br />\n<br />\n判刑：<br />\n裁判官以4星期作量刑起點，接納辯方求情，及考慮到被告開審前主動認罪節省法庭時間，給予四分之一刑期扣減，並下令其中1星期與現正服刑的刑期同期執行。<br />\n‼️本案延長刑期2星期‼️"},{"pid":"c2afe0fab1cce6054dd3ae56771ef101992534b9","tid":2262331,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T04:55:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35adcf76209181305fbb84c0f0673b34269a6b7b","tid":2262331,"uid":11291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T04:56:48.000Z","msg":"推推推推"},{"pid":"0505da81fe506f828aa81ff5d6d6c91b7195dc1c","tid":2262331,"uid":232157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T04:58:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f8cb20744e61c34a6371c12ee03900b84d6c2b6","tid":2262331,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T05:20:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ce27c7f756b2c263265656d3f8531dbf6e4252f","tid":2262331,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T05:36:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff311b7891ad8c06dc7cc4bc6af3b0f7def2145a","tid":2262331,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T08:30:39.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\">他預計明年1月刑滿出獄</span>，希望法庭輕判，讓他可以和家人過農曆新年。裁判官指宣洩情緒並非求情理由，但接納被告沒有預謀，酌情讓本案部份刑期與非法集結案同期執行。<br />\n<br />\n被告去年11月11日涉於理工大學通往紅磡的天橋上以圍欄堵路，他否認襲警及刑事毀壞，上月獲裁定兩罪不成立，但承認非法集結，判監六個月。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201029/AFIEMPRJQREA7KGVS5LLYCW5BY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201029%2FAFIEMPRJQREA7KGVS5LLYCW5BY%2F&d=2u41qa%2Bce9Gslgrzp%2F5KimsgcJLaMXzh2FZp7TjlN88%3D&h=07a37ee0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201029%2FAFIEMPRJQREA7KGVS5LLYCW5BY%2F&h=e5c9ec82\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201029/AFIEMPRJQREA7KGVS5LLYCW5BY/</a>"}]}